            <h2 class="text-left section-header mb-4 text-center"">My System</h2>
                <p class="paragraph--dark text-left font-size-1">The system I use to trade stocks can best be described as a momentum trading system.  The momentum effect in stocks is well documented in respected academic journals, and highlighted in Dr Gray’s book (Quantitative Momentum).  While much of my work uses chart patterns, I also find it is important to pay attention macroeconomic considerations as well.     </p>

                <p class="paragraph--dark text-left font-size-1">The following is a quick overview of how I trade, and is hardly comprehensive.
                </p>

